file.name: swagger.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: neuro_api
servers:
  - url: 'https://aime.teonite.com/'
    description: Main server
  - url: 'http://localhost'
    description: Local server
paths:
  /rest_api/deep_image/transform:
    post:
      summary: Schedules a job to perform zoom or remove jpg artifacts operation
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/applicationName'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Job scheduled successfuly
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Job'
            requestBody:
              content:
                multipart/form-data:
                  schema:
                    type: object
                    properties:
                      transformations:
                        schema:
                          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Transformations'
                      email:
                        type: string
                      fileName:
                        type: string
                        format: binary
        '400':
          description: Error messages include 'Email has not been confirmed', 'User does not have access to this application', 'No such application'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: Email has not been confirmed
                    # TODO: examples don't show up, included possible messages in description
                    # examples:
                    #   email-not-confirmed:
                    #     value: Email has not been confirmed
                    #   no-access-to-app:
                    #     value: User does not have access to this application
                    #   no-app:
                    #     value: No such application
        '403':
          description: Error messages include 'No x-api-key header is provided', 'No x-application-name header is provided', 'No more requests are available. Next requests available DATE'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  message:
                    type: string
                    examples:
                      no-header:
                        value: No x-api-key header is provided
                      no-key:
                        value: No x-application-name header is provided
        '404':
          description: Error messages include 'No user found for provided token', 'No plan found PLAN_NAME'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  message:
                    type: string
                    example: No user found for provided token
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
  /rest_api/deep_image/result/{jobHash}:
    get:
      summary: Returns job result.
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/jobHash'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/applicationName'
      responses:
        '200':
          description:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/JobResult'
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []

  /rest_api/deep_image/configuration:
    get:
      summary: Returns available application configuration regarding to user's current plan.
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/applicationName'
      responses:
        '200':
          description:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Configurations'
      security:
        - ApiKeyAuth: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    ApiKeyAuth:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: X-API-KEY
  parameters:
    applicationName:
      in: header
      name: x-application-name
      schema:
        type: string
        default: 'deep_image'
      required: true
    jobHash:
      in: path
      name: jobHash
      schema:
        type: string

  schemas:
    AuthError:
      type: object
      properties:
        message:
          type: string
          example: No Authorization header is present
    Job:
      type: object
      properties:
        job:
          type: string
    JobResult:
      type: object
      properties:
        status:
          type: string
        result_url:
          type: string
    Configurations:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Configuration'
    Configuration:
      type: object
      properties:
        payload:
          type: object
          properties:
            active_models:
              type: array
              items:
                type: string
                example: [zoom2]

    Transformations:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Transformation'
        example: [zoom2]
    Transformation:
      type: string
      enum:
        - zoom2
        - zoom3
        - zoom4
        - zoom2-jpg50
        - zoom3-jpg50
        - zoom4-jpg50
        - ganzoom2
        - ganzoom3
        - ganzoom4
        - ganzoom2-jpg90
        - ganzoom3-jpg90
        - ganzoom4-jpg90
        - ganzoom4-jpg50
        - jpg
